com.tempodb

Class Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tempodb.Status
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Status
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Information about the success of a single request in an API call that can partially succeed. A bulk write of DataPoints can partially succeed. This object provides information about the cause of the failure for a single request.
    Since:
    1.0.0
